{"tid":129003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[監獄馬] 有個馬字既球員特別容易坐監!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-21T09:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T14:58:10.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7b2a26a996d89ce6f4236207e2cd4f14079aab","tid":129003,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"香港時間2月21日消息，據BBC報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">尼馬為轉會案的上訴請求遭到駁回</span>。根據此前的消息，西班牙國家法院宣佈將重啟尼馬轉會案的調查，而尼馬團隊對此提出上訴，現在遭到了西班牙高等法院的駁回。<span style=\"color: red;\">而檢察官尋求讓尼馬被判監禁兩年</span>，並被罰款800萬英鎊.<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.weloba.com/sites/default/files/images/general/neymar_prison.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weloba.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Fgeneral%2Fneymar_prison.png&h=0afb631a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皇家馬德里的法國前鋒賓施馬（Karim Benzema）涉嫌以性愛短片勒索法國中場華布拿（Mathieu Valbuena）而被捕，他與另外3名嫌疑犯較早前向法庭申請撤銷指控，其中一個要求撤銷指控的原因是警方透過不誠實的方法，令到賓施馬和華布拿的勒索電話對話內容曝光。<br />\n<br />\n不過法國法院周五就拒絕了他們的要求，而一名代表另一名疑犯的律師說，「我們很驚訝，因為該我們希望取消調查的要求被拒絕。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.laligaticketsonline.com/wp-content/uploads/benzema-prison.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.laligaticketsonline.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fbenzema-prison.jpg&h=3301eb43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"051f9b64b4901cd668d11090a031d54bdac951c9","tid":129003,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62ebd8f42579b08f1a2385e5197e35e1d25c31d","tid":129003,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180cca9cb3aee931d51dd73c1bfc858cf943ff8a","tid":129003,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />